      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience that's ready for many more miles. While you'll find some minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age, it remains a dependable and stylish choice for any driver. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a quality car that\u2019s been cared for and is ready for its next adventure!",
