    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a reliable, budget-friendly commuter. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the exterior shows clear signs of use, including some minor paint oxidation on the roof and a few noticeable scratches on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and general wear consistent with its age. It is a solid, functional car that prioritizes utility over cosmetics.",
