    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, likely best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine struggles to start and has a noticeable knock, while the transmission slips significantly when shifting into higher gears. Externally, there is extensive rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling across most surfaces. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. While it currently runs, it will require substantial mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy and reliable.",
